            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This was an unintended effect of two separate changes. Not sure if there is an easy fix (we cannot just restore the NumPy declarations that were intentionally removed to prevent collisions with NumPy's own numpy.pxd), but we should try to keep `cimport numpy.math` working for the time being in order to avoid breaking too much code.\n\nObviously, the eventual right fix for users is to not use `numpy.math` but `libc.math`.",
